title: Gulf of Mexico Tide Predictions
text:
By The Associated Press
Here are the tide predictions from the National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration Ocean Service for principal points along the Gulf of Mexico for Thursday, Oct. 29, 2015.
Galveston - 3:54 a.m. 2.37 H; 10:54 a.m. -0.01 L; 7:16 p.m. 2.79 H
Biloxi Bay - 9:46 a.m. 0.3 L
Vermilion Bay - 4:01 a.m. 1.89 H; 11:26 a.m. -0.01 L; 7:23 p.m. 2.22 H
Atchafalaya Bay (Eugene Island) - 4:08 a.m. 2.32 H; 9:56 a.m. -0.01 L; 7:30 p.m. 2.73 H; 11:13 p.m. 2.12 L
Grand Isle (Barataria Pass) - 12:17 a.m. 1.38 H; 10:30 a.m. 0.12 L
Mississippi River (Southwest Pass) - 8:03 a.m. 0.23 L; 10:45 p.m. 2.0 H
Wine Island - 10:46 a.m. 0.16 L
